gamerule.allowHomeTp.description: Allow players to use commands like /home and /sethome to set and teleport to homes.
gamerule.maxHomes.description: The maximum number of homes that a player can have.
gamerule.allowSpawnTp.description: Allow players to teleport to the world spawn.
gamerule.allowTpa.description: Allow players to teleport to eachother on request using commands like /tpa.
gamerule.tpaRequestTimeout.description: Teleportation requests must be accepted before they time out. This game rule defines the timeout delay in seconds.
gamerule.tpaRequiresSameTeam.description: Set whether teleportation requests may only be sent to players in the same team.
gamerule.tpaMode.description:
Set whether players can teleport themselves to others (/tpa) or call others to themselves (/tpc).
 - TPA: Allow only /tpa
 - TPC: Allow only /tpc
 - Both: Allow both /tpa and /tpc
gamerule.maxNotes.description: Set the maximum number of notes players can make with /note and /notes.
gamerule.deathTp.description:
Sets how players can teleport to their last death location.
 - Off: Disabled.
 - Command: allows /death command, no compass needed.
 - Compass: allows clicking with a recovery compass.
 - Both: allows both a compass and /death.
gamerule.allowPoi.description: Allows players to teleport to shared points of interest.
gamerule.allCanSetPoi.description: Allows all players to configure shared points of interest. If disabled, only admins can set POIs.
gamerule.hidePoiInfo.description: Hides POI info from players. If enabled, only admins can retrieve POI info.
gamerule.teleportPets.description:
Sets whether pets teleport with the player whenever the player teleports. 
 - Off: Not enabled.
 - Dimension: Enabled only in the same dimension.
 - Interdimensional: Enabled through dimensions.
gamerule.teleportLeashedMobs.description:
Sets whether leashed mobs teleport with the player whenever the player teleports. 
 - Off: Not enabled.
 - Dimension: Enabled only in the same dimension.
 - Interdimensional: Enabled through dimensions.
